  "text": "Rabbit polyclonal antibody against chicken gizzard tropomyosin was prepared and characterized as described previously [CITATION_1] . Rabbit polyclonal antibodies against beef heart alpha-actinin or chicken gizzard alpha-actinin were generous gifts from Dr. K . Burridge (University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill) .",
